text: Versam was a municipality of the district of Surselva in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2013, the former municipalities of Versam, Valendas, Safien and Tenna merged into the new municipality of Safiental. ==Other websites== * Official website * Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden Category:2013 disestablishments in Switzerland
